question: What is the rank of HS Prannoy in Badminton World Federation (BWF) World rankings?
explanation: Indian shuttler HS Prannoy got the 17th position in the Badminton World Federation (BWF) World rankings. Ajay Jayaram is ranked 16th, while B Sai Praneeth is 19th place recently. Indian, Kidambi Srikanth is highest ranked at number 8. India now has four shuttlers in top-20.
